Project Summary

Project Information

Field Value
Name GWE's RSE - Record Set Explorer
Description GWE's RSE (Record Set Explorer) is an open source, end user system part of the family of GWE (grid wizard enterprise) products. Its aim is to provide a generic; but powerful and easy to use tool for users to interactively explore record sets. In the context of parameter exploration experiments (domain of the GWE system), such tool is extremely useful, since it allows researchers to review results of such experiments, its set of input parameters and any other structured record set such as results sets obtained from querying XNAT systems.
Homepage http://www.gridwizardenterprise.org
